    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">How Much Soil to Fill a 4x8 Raised Bed?</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-xl font-normal">A practical breakdown of exactly how many bags or cubic yards you need to fill the most popular raised bed size, based on depth.</p>
